org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.rollup

Class EdgeRollUp

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.rollup.RollUp
      • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.rollup.EdgeRollUp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Operator, UnaryGraphToCollectionOperator

    public class EdgeRollUp
extends RollUp
    Applies the groupBy-operator multiple times on a logical graph using different combinations of the given edge grouping keys according to the definition of the rollUp operation in SQL. See the description of the abstract class RollUp for further details.
